31
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:47,390
Mo Sang,

32
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:50,030
I'm going to see Xiangbei.

33
00:01:52,730 --> 00:01:53,420
It's been ten years.

34
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:54,830
