41
00:02:16,670 --> 00:02:17,900
and made so many mistakes.

42
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:21,710
From now on,

43
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:23,710
no matter what she decides,

44
00:02:25,670 --> 00:02:26,940
I have no excuse

45
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:28,180
to leave her.

46
00:02:37,580 --> 00:02:38,390
Look,

47
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,390
I believe in you.

48
00:02:40,570 --> 00:02:41,750
